Frank S. Sklarsky MBA, CPA

Age : 59Public asset : 2,927,575 USDLinked companies : No connection available 





Summary 



Mr. Frank S. Sklarsky is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at PPG Industries, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Harman International Industries, Inc. and Rochester Institute of Technology. Mr. Sklarsky was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Tyco International Ltd., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Eastman Kodak Co., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by ConAgra Foods, Inc., Vice President-Product Finance by DaimlerChrysler Corp., Vice President-Finance by Dell, Inc., and Senior Accountant by Ernst & Young LLP.He received his undergraduate degree from Rochester Institute of Technology and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



